      "content": "i've been sitting here in this apartment for like three days and it hit me today... if i just stopped showing up to the cafe or stopped replying to anyone, it would be weeks before anyone even realized i was gone. like i'm just a ghost here. i don't think anyone would even notice the space i take up.",
