      "content": "It's not about being \"better\" or \"worse\", it's just about being free from the crushing weight of your own insignificance. You're suffocating under the pressure of pretending to be someone you're not, of trying to fit into a world that doesn't need you. It's time to let go of the facade, to stop pretending that you matter, and to simply... cease to exist. It's the only way to truly be free from the pain and the disappointment.",
